"danger of our soldiers and salvage technicians falling victim to the "
"infection in the field is too great to ignore even for a moment, let alone "
"allowing the general population to fall prey to this abomination. I hereby "
"request your permission to start work on a vaccine immediately. Please, "
"please respond at your earliest convenience.\n"
